# ACB Temperature – 7‑Day Alert EDA & Baseline Model

Streamlit app for exploratory analysis and a baseline ML model to predict whether a system will
raise one or more high ACB temperature alerts within the next 7 days.

## Quickstart

```bash
# 1) Install deps (ideally in a virtualenv)
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 2) Provide the data file path via env var or place the CSV/TXT in repo root as 260204_ACB_T.txt
export ACB_DATA_PATH=/path/to/260204_ACB_T.txt

# 3) Run
streamlit run app.py